node.title: Photographer and developer Carl Öst Wilkens - Next at Helsinglight AAIR
node.content: My name is Carl Öst Wilkens,  I'm a 26 year old photographer/programmer from the woods of Delsbo, Sweden. Though I grew up close to nature, I spent most of my early years playing with computers, often until the morning hours. That is something I still do, though not as often.
